Description: Easily interfaces R to spatial datasets available through
        the Victorian Government's WFS (Web Feature Service):
        <https://opendata.maps.vic.gov.au/geoserver/ows?request=GetCapabilities&service=wfs>,
        which allows users to read in 'sf' data from these sources.
        VicmapR uses the lazy querying approach and code developed by
        Teucher et al. (2021) for the 'bcdata' R package
        <doi:10.21105/joss.02927>.
